{"tid":1137378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：修訂逃犯條例理據法、理、情兼備","createTime":"2019-05-03T16:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T01:02:56.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"47fa7be7c8a3adea3ead51965ef4ea61e10ffc4d","tid":1137378,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:56:06.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗表示，律政司及保安局會盡快回應立法會法律顧問就逃犯條例修訂提出的疑問，又強調修例理據法、理、情兼備。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗：「大家知道由台灣事件觸發及有一個制度上的漏洞，我們明顯要堵塞、要完善機制，所以從法律角度，從理、情、彰顯公義的角度都有需要做工夫，保安局及律政司一定會充分回應。反而焦點在立法會條例草案委員會盡早可以展開工作，所以希望明日(星期六)的內委會會議盡快處理有關主席的問題，從而可展開工作，因一日不展開，條例草案委員會大家不能坐下深入交流。」"},{"pid":"16c0c5f3e6f03f354d7eac9b8dbdb90067a02147","tid":1137378,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=346707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346707&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW97O6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=2a412d30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346707&h=fb8e342b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=346707</a>"},{"pid":"fa4a7e1b23b86851311452c658c121f141607a60","tid":1137378,"uid":54681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:56:50.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"0d217a601f2918b29c3fa4e5b5dec685e28f47d5","tid":1137378,"uid":235174,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"冇人在乎張建宗講既野，我相信佢老婆仔女都唔會care呢件廢物 \\<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},{"pid":"c2894b4e3ab066d96ba42a058acde283b9eaefe3","tid":1137378,"uid":44358,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因一日不展開，條例草案委員會大家不能坐下深入交流。</span><br />\n<br />\n一展開，就成為一個有時間限制口水會。最後你有你屌，佢有獻世